je.png |\n  fullname = Fudbalski klub Metalurg Skopje|\n  founded  = {{Start date and age|1964}} |\n  nickname = \u041c\u0435\u0442\u0430\u043b\u0443\u0440\u0446\u0438 (Metallurgists) |\n  ground   = [[\u017delezarnica Stadium]]|\n  capacity = 3,000|\n  chairman = |\n  manager  = |\n  league   = |\n  season = [[2016\u201317 Macedonian Second Football League|2016\u201317]] |\n  position = [[Macedonian Second Football League|Macedonian Second League]], 9th (relegated) |\npattern_la1=|pattern_b1=_whitethinlines|pattern_so1=_blacktop|\n leftarm1=008000|body1=008000|rightarm1=008000|shorts1=008000|socks1=008000|\n  pattern_la2=_shouldersonwhite|pattern_b2=_shouldersonwhite|pattern_ra2=_shouldersonwhite|\n  leftarm2=FFFFFF|body2=FFFFFF|rightarm2=FFFFFF|shorts2=FFFFFF|socks2=FFFFFF|\n| website = https://web.archive.org/web/20110717083732/http://www.fcmetalurg.com.mk/\n}}\n\n'''FK Metalurg''' ({{lang-mk|\u0424\u041a \u041c\u0435\u0442\u0430\u043b\u0443\u0440\u0433}}) is a football club from [[Skopje]], [[North Macedonia]]. They were recently competed in the [[Macedonian Second Football League|Macedonian Second League]].\n\n==History==\nThe club was founded in 1964.\n\nMetalurg has entered the [[Macedonian First Football League|Macedonian First League]] in the 1992\u201393 season and were relegated the same year. After playing 15 seasons in the [[Macedonian Second Football League|Macedonian Second League]] they were back in the Macedonian First League for the 2008\u201309 season. In the 2009\u201310 season they finished in 3rd place and played in Europe for the first time in club history.<ref>[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2011/matches/round=2000124/match=2002580/postmatch/commentary/index.html Qaraba\u011f&nbsp;\u2013 Metalurg Skopje] UEFA.com {{in lang|en}}</ref> In 2015\u201316 season Metalurg was relegated from the First League after 8 seasons.\n\n==Season-by-season record==\nA '''season-by-season record''' of Metalurg league performances:\n\n{| class=wikit