ovember 16, 2011 (Alvin y las Ardillas) (Spain)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Also on April 1, 2008, a Blu-ray \"gift set\" that included dolls of all the three chipmunks alongside the movie was released.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Rockin-Blu-ray-Gift-Set-with-Chipmuck-Plush-Dolls-Blu-ray/113259/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Rockin' Blu-ray Gift Set with Chipmuck Plush Dolls Blu-ray Release Date April 1, 2008|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> On [[Amazon Prime]], the film was originally released in standard definition on March 30, 2010<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/prime/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Prime-Video/1089/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Prime Release Date March 30, 2010|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> before being issued in HD on September 18, 2012;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/prime/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-HD-Prime-Video/11582/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks HD Prime Release Date September 18, 2012|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> and it was made available on [[Movies Anywhere]] on October 12, 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/ma/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Movies-Anywhere/95/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Movies Anywhere Release Date October 12, 2017|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref>\n\nVarious home collections of [[Alvin and the Chipmunks in film|''Alvin and the Chipmunks'' films]] have been released by Fox, all of which at least have the first film. Blu-ray sets including both ''Alvin and the Chipmunks'' and ''[[Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel|The Squeakquel]]'' (2009) were released in the United Kingdom on April 12, 2010,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Double-Trouble-Pack-Blu-ray/9911/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks: Double Trouble Pack Blu-ray Release Date April 12, 2010 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel) (United Kingdom)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> France on April 23, 2010,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-and-Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks--The-Squeakquel-Blu-ray/10301/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks : The Squeakquel Blu-ray Release Date April 23, 2010 (Alvin et les Chipmunks / Alvin et les Chipmunks 2) (Frace)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Germany on May 7, 2010,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-and-Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-The-Squeakquel-Blu-ray/9879/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel Blu-ray Release Date May 7, 2010 (Alvin und die Chipmunks: Teil 1+2) (Germany)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Sweden on May 12, 2010,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-1-and-2-Blu-ray/76523/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks 1 & 2 Blu-ray Release Date May 12, 2010 (Alvin och G\u00e4nget 1 & 2) (Sweden)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Australia on June 2, 2010 (an edition that came with a Digital file of both films),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-1-and-2-Blu-ray/13193/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks 1 and 2 Blu-ray Release Date June 2, 2010 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel) (Australia)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> and North America on March 5, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-1-and-Alvin-2-Blu-ray/96289/|title=Alvin 1 + Alvin 2 Blu-ray Release Date March 5, 2013 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-1-and-Alvin-2-Blu-ray/64536/|title=Alvin 1 + Alvin 2 Blu-ray Release Date March 5, 2013 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel) (Canada)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-and-Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-2-The-Squeakquel-Blu-ray/116783/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks 2: The Squeakquel Blu-ray Release Date March 5, 2013 (Alvin y las ardillas 1 y 2) (Mexico)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Blu-ray sets that feature the first two ''Alvin'' films plus ''[[Alvin and the Chipmunks: Chipwrecked|Chipwrecked]]'' (2011) were released in Finland on March 23, 2012,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-1-3-Blu-ray/139999/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks 1-3 Blu-ray Release Date March 23, 2012 (Alvin ja pikkuoravat 1-3) (Finland)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> the United Kingdom on April 2, 2012 (which came with digital files of all films),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Collection-Blu-ray/37432/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Collection Blu-ray Release Date April 2, 2012 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel / Alvin and the Chipmunks: Chip-wrecked <nowiki>|</nowiki> Triple Play) (United Kingdom)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Germany on April 20, 2012,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Box-Set-Blu-ray/36984/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Box Set Blu-ray Release Date April 20, 2012 (Alvin und die Chipmunks \u2013 Teil 1-3) (Germany)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Australia on May 30, 2012,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Triple-Pack-Blu-ray/42881/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Triple Pack Blu-ray Release Date May 30, 2012 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel / Alvin and the Chipmunks: Chip-wrecked) (Australia)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Sweden on June 13, 2012,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-1-2-and-3-Blu-ray/46188/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks 1, 2 & 3 Blu-ray Release Date June 13, 2012 (Alvin och G\u00e4nget 1, 2 & 3) (Sweden)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> the United States on March 5, 2013,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Trilogy-Blu-ray/73207/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Trilogy Blu-ray Release Date March 5, 2013 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / The Squeakquel / Chipwrecked)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Mexico on the same day,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Trilogy-Blu-ray/90488/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Trilogy Blu-ray Release Date March 5, 2013 (Trilog\u00eda Alvin y las ardillas) (Mexico)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> and Canada on October 8, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-1-3-Blu-ray/81607/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks 1-3 Blu-ray Release Date October 8, 2013 (Bilingual <nowiki>|</nowiki> Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel / Alvin and the Chipmunks 3: Chipwrecked) (Canada)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> A collection of the trilogy was released on the [[iTunes Store]] on December 11, 2012.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/itunes/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Triple-Pack-iTunes/9362/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Triple Pack iTunes Release Date December 11, 2012 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / The Squeakquel / Chipwrecked)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Blu-rays including all four ''Alvin'' films, including ''[[Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip|The Road Chip]]'' (2015), were released in Hong Kong on April 14, 2016,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-4-Movie-Collection-B