g on July 18, 2008;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Blu-ray/245241/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Blu-ray Release Date July 18, 2008 (Hong Kong)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Taiwan on August 8, 2008;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Blu-ray/245277/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Blu-ray Release Date August 8, 2008 (Taiwan)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> France on November 19, 2008;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Blu-ray/10300/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Blu-ray Release Date November 19, 2008 (Alvin et les Chipmunks) (France)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Denmark on December 19, 2009;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Blu-ray/44240/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Blu-ray Release Date December 19, 2009 (Alvin og de Fr\u00e6kke Jordegern \u2013 Rock Hero Edition) (Denmark)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Canada on March 29, 2011;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Blu-ray/4679/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Blu-ray Release Date March 29, 2011 (Canada)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Mexico on October 16, 2011;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Blu-ray/90486/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Blu-ray Release Date October 11, 2011 (Alvin y las ardillas) (Mexico)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> and Spain on November 16, 2011.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-Blu-ray/33638/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks Blu-ray Release Date November 16, 2011 (Alvin y las Ardillas) (Spain)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Also on April 1, 2008, a Blu-ray \"gift set\" that included dolls of all the three chipmunks alongside the movie was