nd-the-Chipmunks--The-Squeakquel-Blu-ray/10301/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks : The Squeakquel Blu-ray Release Date April 23, 2010 (Alvin et les Chipmunks / Alvin et les Chipmunks 2) (Frace)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Germany on May 7, 2010,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-and-Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-The-Squeakquel-Blu-ray/9879/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel Blu-ray Release Date May 7, 2010 (Alvin und die Chipmunks: Teil 1+2) (Germany)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Sweden on May 12, 2010,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-1-and-2-Blu-ray/76523/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks 1 & 2 Blu-ray Release Date May 12, 2010 (Alvin och G\u00e4nget 1 & 2) (Sweden)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> Australia on June 2, 2010 (an edition that came with a Digital file of both films),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-1-and-2-Blu-ray/13193/|title=Alvin and the Chipmunks 1 and 2 Blu-ray Release Date June 2, 2010 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel) (Australia)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref> and North America on March 5, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-1-and-Alvin-2-Blu-ray/96289/|title=Alvin 1 + Alvin 2 Blu-ray Release Date March 5, 2013 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-1-and-Alvin-2-Blu-ray/64536/|title=Alvin 1 + Alvin 2 Blu-ray Release Date March 5, 2013 (Alvin and the Chipmunks / Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel) (Canada)|website=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-and-Alvin-and-the-Chipmunks-2